headline: TT Q1 Earnings Call: Trane Technologies Exceeds Expectations, Focuses on Pricing Amid Tariffs
summary: HVAC company Trane (NYSE:TT) reported Q1 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 11.2% year on year to $4.69 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.41 per share was 9.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
